#          
word_network <- function(x) {
  ggraph(x,                                   #     
         layout = "fr") +                     #   
    geom_edge_link(color = "gray50",          # () 
                   alpha = 0.5) +             # () 
    geom_node_point(color = "lightcoral",     #  
                    size = 5) +               #  
    geom_node_text(aes(label = name),         #   
                   repel = T,                 #   ->   
                   size = 5,                  #  
                   family = "nanumgothic") +  # 
    theme_graph()                             #  
}
# 
set.seed(1234)                                # Seed  ->     
word_network(graph_comment)

# 1.      
set.seed(1234)                                    # Seed  -> For group_infomap()
graph_cors <- word_cors %>%                       #      in 3-1-2
  filter(correlation >= 0.15) %>%                 #   0.15     ->   
  as_tbl_graph(directed = F) %>%                  #     / directed = F :    X
  mutate(centrality = centrality_degree(),        # centrality_degree :   
         group = as.factor(group_infomap()))      # group_infomap :   / as.factor : Factor  ->      


set.seed(1234)                                    # Seed  ->     
ggraph(graph_cors, 
      layout = "fr") +                            #   
  geom_edge_link(color = "gray50",                # () 
                 aes(edge_alpha = correlation,    # ()  ->       
                     edge_width = correlation),   # ()  ->       
                 show.legend = F) +               #  
  scale_edge_width(range = c(1, 4)) +             #   
  geom_node_point(aes(size = centrality,          #   ->
